name: Ryan Haywood Twitch Stream Archive
profile:
This is a channel to archive all of Ryan Haywood's twitch streams.

If you wanna join us live check out  https://www.twitch.tv/sortamaliciousgaming

Regular streams are Tuesdays and Thursdays at 8pm Central time. Follow Ryan on Twitter @RyanTheTwit for other stream times.

The channel is run by community member M3gaShiny with approval from Ryan Haywood who also owns the channel. Videos will be released one month after bring streamed on twitch.

If you have any concerns or questions feel free to message MegaShiny on Twitter / M3gaShiny on Discord

If you wanna be a part of the community, you are welcome to join us in the Madhouse Misfits Discord! 

Here is the invite link! See you there!
https://discord.gg/sortamaliciousmisfits
